author: The Associated Press
title: The top iPhone and iPad apps on App Store
text:
App Store Official Charts for the week ending October 12, 2015:
Top Paid iPhone Apps:
1. Minecraft: Pocket Edition, Mojang
2. hocus., Yunus Ayyildiz
3. Plague Inc., Ndemic Creations
4. Geometry Dash, RobTop Games AB
5. Heads Up!, Warner Bros.
6. PAUSE - Relaxation at your fingertip, ustwo
7. PewDiePie: Legend of the Brofist, Outerminds Inc.
8. New Emoji - Extra Emoji Stickers, Emoji Apps GmbH
9. Purify Blocker: No Ads. No Tracking. Lightning-Fast Safari., Chris Aljoudi
10. Bloons TD 5, Ninja Kiwi
Top Free iPhone Apps:
1. Smashy Road: Wanted, Remco Kortenoever
2. Messenger, Facebook, Inc.
3. Facebook, Facebook, Inc.
4. YouTube, Google, Inc.
5. Snapchat, Snapchat, Inc.
6. Instagram, Instagram, Inc.
7. Need for Speed No Limits, Electronic Arts
8. Pandora - Free Music & Radio, Pandora Media, Inc.
9. Netflix, Netflix, Inc.
10. Google Maps, Google, Inc.
Top Paid iPad Apps:
1. Minecraft: Pocket Edition, Mojang
2. Lucky Craft ( Build Battle Edition )- BLOCK MINI GAME Survival Hunter with Multiplayer, Patyi Kati
3. Geometry Dash, RobTop Games AB
4. PewDiePie: Legend of the Brofist, Outerminds Inc.
5. Terraria, 505 Games (US), Inc.
6. Plague Inc., Ndemic Creations
7. Scribblenauts Remix, Warner Bros.
8. Sago Mini Babies, Sago Sago
9. Five Nights at Freddys 4, Scott Cawthon
10. Super Sharp, 1Button SARL
Top Free iPad Apps:
1. Smashy Road: Wanted, Remco Kortenoever
2. Netflix, Netflix, Inc.
3. Need for Speed No Limits, Electronic Arts
4. Sonic Dash 2: Sonic Boom, SEGA
5. YouTube, Google, Inc.
6. Messenger, Facebook, Inc.
7. Calculator for iPad Free, International Travel Weather Calculator
8. Shooty Skies - Endless Arcade Flyer, Mighty Games
9. Google, Google, Inc.
10. The Walking Dead: No Man's Land, Next Games Oy
